### Welcome to Zining Wang's Homepage!


### Myself
My name is Zining Wang. My Chinese name is 王梓宁. I’m a junior in [Emory University](http://www.emory.edu). I am pursuing double majors in Applied Math (BS) and Computer Science (BS). 

![](http://d.hiphotos.baidu.com/shitu/pic/item/55e736d12f2eb938f85f56f5d2628535e5dd6f82.jpg)

### Skills and Coursework
Math: Mathematic modeling, Statistics, Optimization, Numerical Analysis, Matrix Theory
Computer Science: Java, Python, C, Sql, R Programming
Language: Fluent Chinese, fluent English, Intermediate French

### Hobbies
Basketball, Table Tennis, Cooking

### Contact
My email address is emorywangzining@gmail.com. Feel free to contact me!
